sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Inst as Institution User
  participant UI as Institution Workspace UI
  participant WF as Workflow Engine
  participant Doc as Document Service
  participant OCR as OCR Connector
  participant CE as Compliance Connector
  participant RE as Research Connector
  participant RV as Review Service
  participant AU as Audit Service
  participant EX as Export Service

  Inst->>UI: Submit contract intake package
  UI->>WF: Start workflow(contract-intake-review)
  WF->>AU: Record event intake_received
  WF->>Doc: Create matter/document records
  Doc->>AU: Record document_ingested

  WF->>OCR: Request OCR extraction (async)
  OCR-->>WF: OCR text + confidence + artifacts
  WF->>AU: Record ocr_completed

  WF->>CE: Resolve obligations/clauses and run compliance check
  CE-->>WF: Findings, risks, issue log candidates
  WF->>AU: Record compliance_analysis_completed

  WF->>RE: Optional legal citation enrichment
  RE-->>WF: Citation cards and confidence scores
  WF->>RV: Create review task bundle
  RV-->>UI: Review queue updated

  Inst->>UI: Approve / request changes / escalate
  UI->>RV: Submit review decision
  RV->>WF: Decision event
  WF->>AU: Record decision and actor context

  alt Approved
    WF->>EX: Generate export package
    EX-->>WF: Export artifact URI
    WF->>AU: Record exported
  else Changes requested
    WF->>RV: Re-open task and assign follow-up
    WF->>AU: Record changes_requested
  end

  WF-->>UI: Final workflow state and trace_id
